#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

typedef long long ll;
typedef vector<ll> vll;
typedef pair<ll,ll> pll;
typedef vector<pll> vpll;

int main() {
  ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
  int test;
  cin >> test;
  while(test--) {
    int n;
    ll l;
    cin >> n >> l;
    
    vpll V(n + 1);
    for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) { 
      cin >> V[i].first;
      V[i].second = i;
    }
    
    V[n].first = l + 1;
    V[n].second = n;
    
    if (n > 100) {
      cout << -1 << endl;
      continue;
    }
    
    sort(V.begin(), V.end());
    
    vll R(n + 1);
    
    bool tt = true;
    if (V[0].first != 1 or V[n].second != n) tt = false;
    
    for (int i = 1; i <= n and tt; ++i) {
      if (2*V[i - 1].first - 1 < V[i].first) {
	if ((V[i].first - V[i - 1].first)%V[i - 1].first == 0){
	  R[V[i - 1].second] = (V[i].first - V[i - 1].first)/V[i - 1].first;
	  if (R[V[i - 1].second] == 0) tt = false;
	}
	else tt = false;
      }
      else tt = false;
    }
    
    if (!tt) cout << -1 << endl;
    else {
      for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) cout << (i? " " : "") << R[i];
      cout << endl;
    }
  }
}
